Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: first updates now
des:
First Updates Now focuses on the latest and most popular news, discussions, people, and events in the First Robotics Community. This skill presents the most up to date statistics taken live from The Blue Alliance.
In accordance with The Blue Alliance's Developer Guidelines, here is their site. https://www.thebluealliance.com
(This skill has no affiliation with The Blue Alliance and only sends necessary information to their API in which no personal information is included with that request)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
